         </a>
      </div>
      <div xmlns="" class="item">
         <div style="padding: 1px; padding-left: 8px;" class="tested">
            <a name="Tea_for_Flu">
               <h4>Tea for Flu</h4>
            </a>
            <div style="display: inline; text-align: right; width: 100%;">
					| <a href="#top">top</a>
            </div>
            <br/>
            <p class="comment">7/10 | 02/09/2002 | takes 10 mins, makes 1 cup</p>
         </div>
         <div class="contents">
            <table border="0" cellspacing="3px" id="ig3">
               <tbody>
				
                  <tbody class="group" valign="top">
                     <tr valign="top">
                        <td class="group_cell" rowspan="3">A</td>
                     </tr>
					
                     <tr>
                        <td>2 tsp Fresh Sage</td>
                     </tr>
					
                     <tr class="even">
                        <td>1 cup Boiling Water</td>
                     </tr>
				
                  </tbody>
				
                  <tbody class="group" valign="top">
                     <tr valign="top">
                        <td class="group_cell" rowspan="4">B</td>
                     </tr>
					
                     <tr>
                        <td>  Juice of 1 Lemon</td>
                     </tr>
					
                     <tr class="even">
                        <td>a pinch Cayenne Pepper</td>
                     </tr>
					
                     <tr>
                        <td>1 tsp Honey</td>
                     </tr>
				
                  </tbody>
			
               </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>
				Put sage into a cup, add boiling water. Leave for steep for 10 mins.
				Strain and add 'B', stir and drink hot.
			</p>
            <p class="icomment">
			
            </p>
         </div>
